OL,4,C'middle-class women of a certain age'
OL,6,FThe 60-year-old responded to the
OL,7,Fallegations against him in a video
OL,8,Fposted on Instagram, claiming he had
OL,9,Fworked with thousands of contestants
OL,10,Ffrom different ages and walks of life,
OL,11,Fbut is only aware of 13 complaints.
OL,13,FHe continued: "I can see the
OL,14,Fcomplaints coming from a handful of
OL,15,Fmiddle-class women of a certain age,
OL,16,Fjust from Celebrity MasterChef. This
OL,17,Fisn't right.
