OL,3,CGregg Wallace says accusations made by
OL,4,C'middle-class women of a certain age'
OL,6,F"In 20 years, over 20 years of
OL,7,Ftelevision, can you imagine how many
OL,8,Fwomen, female contestants on
OL,9,FMasterChef, have made sexual remarks,
OL,10,For sexual innuendo? Can you imagine?"
OL,12,FIn the latest allegations, Wallace was
OL,13,Faccused of making lewd comments and
OL,14,Fasking for the personal phone numbers
OL,15,Fof female production staff in a letter
OL,16,Fa producer and director claimed to
OL,17,Fhave sent to the BBC in 2022.
