OL,4,C'middle-class women of a certain age'
OL,6,FThe letter, posted to Instagram by
OL,7,FDawn Elrick on her Sh*t Men In TV Have
OL,8,FSaid To Me account, collected a number
OL,9,Fof anonymous reports from people who
OL,10,Falleged they "have experienced sexism
OL,11,Fand sexual harassment within the TV
OL,12,Findustry".
OL,14,FIt comes after it was announced that
OL,15,FWallace is to step away from the BBC
OL,16,Fcooking show while historical
OL,17,Fmisconduct complaints are externally
OL,18,Freviewed by MasterChef producer
OL,19,FBanijay UK.
